OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1772301852
OL,3,CHospice turning dying patients away
OL,4,Cbecause it can't afford to keep beds
OL,5,Copen
OL,7,FA hospice near Swindon says it is
OL,8,Fbeing forced to turn away dying
OL,9,Fpatients every week because it can't
OL,10,Fafford to keep all of its specialist
OL,11,Fbeds open.
OL,13,FProspect Hospice says a lack of NHS
OL,14,Ffunding means half its inpatient unit
OL,15,Fis closed and that means some people
OL,16,Fare having to spend their final days
OL,17,Fin hospital instead.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
